
GERBER {GRB} BUYS <acqabr>GERBER SYSTEMS</acqabr> {<acqcode>GSTI</acqcode>} SHARES
    SOUTH WINDSOR, Conn, March 12 - Gerber Scientific Inc said
its <purchaser>GST Acquisition Corp</purchaser> <status>purchased</status> 444,646 shares of its 84 pct
owned <acquired>Gerber Systems Technology</acquired> pursuant to a January 15 tender
offer.
    Following the purchase, Gerber made a capital contribution
to <purchabr>GST</purchabr> of all the shares it owned resulting in 95.6 pct
